{"tid":1799650,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實我地係咪應該由黃色經濟圈既機會，反思一下我地以前既消費習慣","createTime":"2019-12-27T06:15:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-27T11:36:14.000Z","uid":188176,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"126199addccf033c32bf7c750522cc5567174b94","tid":1799650,"uid":188176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T06:15:33.000Z","msg":"唔知由幾時開始，香港人窮到得番錢甚至係錢都無<br />\n現代家庭甚至唔識亦唔會煮飯，日日出街食<br />\n養左一大堆垃圾飲食店出黎<br />\n而香港人除左番工外係完全無興趣可言<br />\n講緊係以外國為例子，可以係打機，可以係釣魚，可以係做手工<br />\n香港人問佢興趣係乜好多人都答唔出<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n只會由買野填補空虛既心靈<br />\n我地係唔係應該反思下，我地既生活習慣係有d問題"},{"pid":"fcb4a2a23ad6518b441dfd575d34389905449ed6","tid":1799650,"uid":286711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T08:08:12.000Z","msg":"借個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[黃色商品圈] 新職業 - 標價師<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1798559\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1798559</a>"},{"pid":"89ee77fc69935c9a963efe43ee0b997645554389","tid":1799650,"uid":188176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T11:26:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa1c3cdf4ac599cd6602ceb33b07982d2596250a","tid":1799650,"uid":7125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T11:36:14.000Z","msg":"咁係時間問題姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大佬人地有時收工番到屋企都未日落 香港番到屋企沖埋涼就預備訓架啦"}]}